                <head>No. 54<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On June 1, 1953, Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_DJF2">Dulles</persName>
                    delivered a report on the Near East over radio and television networks. The
                    report is printed in Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, June
                    15, 1953, pages 831–835, and is also published as Department of State
                    publication 5088.</p>
            </div>
